snippet.title: IRON LUNG Official Trailer (2026) Mark Fischbach, Troy Baker
snippet.description:
Official Iron Lung Movie Trailer 2026 | More ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/App | Markiplier Movie Trailer | Cinema: 30 Jan 2026 | Details ➤ https://KinoCheck.com/movie/y25/iron-lung-2026?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=description
An ocean of blood. The only hope left after The Quiet Rapture. In the rusting halls of crumbling space stations, the last remnants of humanity craft a submarine to explore the bleeding depths... and weld one soul inside to pilot it. But hope in this void is as illusionary as the starlight. This is not an expedition. It's an execution.

Iron Lung (2026) is the new horror movie starring Troy Baker, Mark Fischbach and Caroline Kaplan.
